<paragraph id="8BD98973363C151EFF2C9BD1FB95FEA0" blockId="2.[151,1437,150,321]" pageId="2" pageNumber="289">
<emphasis id="B9125561363C151EFF2C9BD1FEDEFF51" bold="true" box="[151,323,150,176]" pageId="2" pageNumber="289">Adult habitus.</emphasis>
General color yellowish brown, head mostly light yellowish brown; triocellate, ocelli white, black surrounded the inner base of the circles, light brown bands connected the mid-ocellus and two posterior ocelli, anterior ocellus smaller, posterior ocelli closer to each other than to the eyes; antennae dark brown; palpi yellow brown (
<figureCitation id="135D95F6363C151EFF559A44FEB2FEFC" box="[238,303,259,285]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="2.[151,250,923,947]" captionTargetBox="[149,1438,342,896]" captionTargetId="figure-105@2.[149,1438,342,896]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURE 1. Claassenia magna Wu, 1948. Male adult, dorsal view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6592803" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6592803/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="289">Fig. 1</figureCitation>
). Pronotum elliptical, middle longitudinal line were dark brown, surface rugose (
<figureCitation id="135D95F6363C151EFB019A44FB62FEFC" box="[1210,1279,259,285]" captionStart="FIGURE 2" captionStartId="2.[151,250,1943,1967]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,971,1920]" captionTargetId="figure-118@2.[151,1436,971,1920]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURE 2. Claassenia magna Wu, 1948. Male head and pronotum, dorsal view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6592805" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6592805/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="289">Fig. 2</figureCitation>
). Legs yellow brown, femorotibial joint darker. Wings translucent, veins dark brown (
<figureCitation id="135D95F6363C151EFC0E9A60FC6AFEA0" box="[949,1015,295,321]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="2.[151,250,923,947]" captionTargetBox="[149,1438,342,896]" captionTargetId="figure-105@2.[149,1438,342,896]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURE 1. Claassenia magna Wu, 1948. Male adult, dorsal view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6592803" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6592803/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="289">Fig. 1</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
