</taxonomicName>
. A. Female head and pronotum, dorsal view; B. Female terminalia, dorsal view; C. Female terminalia, ventral view.
</paragraph>
</caption>
<paragraph id="8BD98973363A1518FF7C9C47FDCAF8DF" blockId="4.[151,1437,1791,2034]" pageId="4" pageNumber="291">
<emphasis id="B9125561363A1518FF7C9C47FF6BF8FB" bold="true" box="[199,246,1792,1818]" pageId="4" pageNumber="291">Egg</emphasis>
. Length ca. 
<quantity id="4C9E2496363A1518FE379DB8FE68F8FB" box="[396,501,1791,1818]" metricMagnitude="-4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.1" pageId="4" pageNumber="291" unit="mm" value="0.51">0.51 mm</quantity>
, width ca. 
<quantity id="4C9E2496363A1518FDC29C47FD7CF8FB" box="[633,737,1792,1818]" metricMagnitude="-4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.8" pageId="4" pageNumber="291" unit="mm" value="0.38">0.38 mm</quantity>
(n = 1). Spindle-shaped, collar wide. Chorion covered with shallow pits and without ridges (
<figureCitation id="135D95F6363A1518FDBE9C64FDD4F8DF" box="[517,585,1827,1854]" captionStart="FIGURE 7" captionStartId="5.[151,250,1185,1209]" captionTargetBox="[152,1436,417,1162]" captionTargetId="figure-126@5.[152,1436,417,1162]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURE 7. Claassenia magna Wu, 1948. A. Egg and collar, lateral view; B. Egg, surface details." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6592816" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6592816/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="291">Fig. 7</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
